rComments: Great prof! So enthusiastic about the topic and pain research. I would totally take his course again!

Greatly disappointed at how the course was handled. Assessments did not reflect the purpose of HMB422 as he focused on Neuroscience & not Health and Disease. Good lectures, but tests unnecessarily detailed & did not focus on general concepts to be learned from course. Harshly deducts marks despite strictly following instructions. Reconsider taking.
